  {
    "type": "list",
    "sub_type": "text",
    "list_items": [
      "·Thedeploymentandtrainingof neuralnetworks on edge computingdevicesposemanychallenges. ",
      "·The lowmemory nature of edgedevices isoften one of thebiggest limitingfactorsencounteredinthedeploymentof largeneural networkmodels. ",
      "·Tensorrematerializationorrecomputeisawaytoaddress high memoryrequirements forneuralnetworktrainingandinference ",
      "·In this paperwe consider the problem of execution time minimizationof computegraphssubjecttoamemory budget. ",
      "·Inparticular，wedevelopanewconstraintprogramming formulation calledMoccasinwith only O(n) integervariables, wherenisthenumberof nodesinthecompute graph(asopposed topriorwork formulationswith $O ( n ^ { 2 } )$ variables). "
    ],
    "bbox": [
